WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: zh-CN

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
MkvDrama.Org

01:35.280 --> 01:37.840
Episode 11

01:44.920 --> 01:46.360
Why don't you take the carriage?

01:48.240 --> 01:49.800
I have something to ask you, Master.

01:51.720 --> 01:52.720
What?

01:53.840 --> 01:54.840
What did you mean

01:55.320 --> 01:58.480
when you said what you said in Zhong's Garden?

02:02.200 --> 02:03.360
Anyway

02:03.800 --> 02:05.640
thank you for not sending me

02:05.720 --> 02:07.880
to the Junior Lord of Wu family.

02:08.240 --> 02:10.440
But you already have a wife.

02:11.000 --> 02:12.920
You can ask me to do anything in return

02:14.160 --> 02:16.560
except marrying you.

02:18.800 --> 02:20.000
What if I don't have a wife?

02:30.800 --> 02:33.640
I married Hua Qian because she drugged me.

02:34.280 --> 02:35.280
I was forced to take responsibility.

02:35.360 --> 02:36.360
I had no knowledge of me being drugged.

02:36.760 --> 02:38.000
I've never touched her.

02:38.600 --> 02:40.360
She admitted to it herself.

02:43.000 --> 02:44.880
That sounds like something she would do.

02:45.440 --> 02:48.920
Now I know what I want.

02:51.640 --> 02:52.920
Give me some time.

02:53.440 --> 02:55.800
After your father's case is settled

02:55.880 --> 02:57.360
I will formally divorce her.

03:00.400 --> 03:01.640
After all...

03:02.680 --> 03:04.240
this is her wish as well.

03:04.720 --> 03:05.720
Her...

03:06.840 --> 03:08.200
wish?

03:09.880 --> 03:11.600
Do you know the Junior Lord of Wu family?

03:13.360 --> 03:14.520
No.

03:15.120 --> 03:17.240
I just met him once

03:17.560 --> 03:19.440
and I didn't know his identity then.

03:19.880 --> 03:22.120
I never thought we would see each other again.

03:26.960 --> 03:28.120
How is the investigation

03:28.600 --> 03:29.920
into your father's case?

03:30.440 --> 03:32.640
In addition to mentioning

03:32.720 --> 03:35.160
how the Ge family committed the fraud

03:35.440 --> 03:37.000
my father told me in a letter

03:37.080 --> 03:38.120
that when he was in prison

03:38.200 --> 03:41.240
he received an anonymous letter saying

03:41.320 --> 03:42.480
"There is ample time ahead.

03:42.560 --> 03:43.720
Take care of yourself."

03:44.480 --> 03:45.880
This person must know

03:45.960 --> 03:47.320
some inside information

03:47.680 --> 03:50.080
but I haven't found out who he is yet.

03:51.720 --> 03:53.360
Why didn't I hear you mention it before?

03:55.760 --> 03:56.760
I...

03:58.400 --> 04:00.760
You thought I wasn't worthy of your trust?

04:02.840 --> 04:04.760
By the way, I managed to reach

04:04.840 --> 04:07.240
a former maid of mine a few days ago.

04:07.600 --> 04:09.760
She provided me with a lot of information

04:10.240 --> 04:11.960
but most of it is useless.

04:12.040 --> 04:13.120
Your maid?

04:13.440 --> 04:14.920
She used to be a servant of my family

04:15.000 --> 04:16.320
but was sold to someone else.

04:17.600 --> 04:20.040
It took me a lot of effort to find her

04:20.880 --> 04:22.240
but she refused to be my maid again.

04:23.240 --> 04:24.240
Why?

04:25.400 --> 04:26.400
Who knows?

04:27.680 --> 04:30.280
After all, to each their own.

04:30.880 --> 04:32.400
Nothing can be forced.

04:33.400 --> 04:34.480
Forced?

04:35.640 --> 04:36.640
That's right.

05:01.240 --> 05:02.240
It's me.

05:05.080 --> 05:07.080
Can we talk first?

05:07.480 --> 05:08.600
I have nothing to say

05:08.680 --> 05:09.800
to the Junior Lord of Wu family.

05:11.000 --> 05:12.440
Are you angry

05:12.520 --> 05:14.320
because of my identity

05:14.680 --> 05:16.480
or because I kept my real identity from you?

05:16.560 --> 05:17.560
What do you mean?

05:17.880 --> 05:18.960
Aren't they the same?

05:20.960 --> 05:21.960
Nothing.

05:22.520 --> 05:23.720
I was just teasing you.

05:23.800 --> 05:25.720
What's your motive for coming to me?

05:26.960 --> 05:28.160
I swear

05:28.240 --> 05:29.880
I fell in love with you at first sight

05:30.280 --> 05:31.840
and can't stop thinking about you.

05:31.920 --> 05:33.080
Stop that!

05:33.160 --> 05:34.280
I'm serious.

05:35.240 --> 05:37.800
It's like fate.

05:38.320 --> 05:41.120
I can't forget you since our first meeting.

05:41.440 --> 05:43.800
If this is all that you want to say today

05:44.320 --> 05:45.520
then I suggest you leave now.

05:46.480 --> 05:48.000
You really want to be with Zhong Yelan?

05:49.920 --> 05:51.400
It beats being with you.

05:51.480 --> 05:53.000
He already has a wife.

05:53.840 --> 05:54.920
Are you leaving or not?

05:55.000 --> 05:56.000
What if I told you

05:56.080 --> 05:57.080
I could clear your father's name?

05:57.160 --> 05:58.520
Do you think I will believe you?

05:59.040 --> 06:00.200
I'll count to three.

06:00.280 --> 06:02.880
If you don't leave, I'll scream.

06:03.640 --> 06:05.120
Are you really going to do this?

06:05.200 --> 06:06.200
One.

06:06.280 --> 06:08.880
Haven't you wondered why I keep pestering you?

06:08.960 --> 06:09.960
Two.

06:10.040 --> 06:11.440
You will come to me in the future.

06:11.520 --> 06:12.520
Three.

06:25.920 --> 06:26.960
Master.

06:27.240 --> 06:28.800
Do I still need to send the invitation card

06:28.880 --> 06:30.160
to Mistress Zhong?

06:32.800 --> 06:34.720
Seems like she really doesn't know.

06:35.840 --> 06:37.880
Yes. Send it to Zhong Residence

06:37.960 --> 06:38.960
early tomorrow morning.

06:41.880 --> 06:43.880
What? Is there anything else?

06:44.320 --> 06:45.400
Master.

06:46.520 --> 06:47.880
You have found out the truth.

06:48.480 --> 06:50.200
Are you still going to take her away?

06:50.280 --> 06:52.600
Yeah. She intrigues me

06:53.160 --> 06:55.320
more and more.

06:55.840 --> 06:58.200
But Mistress Zhong is a married woman.

06:59.000 --> 07:02.080
I'm afraid she won't come out to meet you.

07:02.160 --> 07:04.080
I'm sending her a proper invite

07:04.160 --> 07:05.840
and she's not an unmarried woman.

07:06.200 --> 07:07.480
There's no reason why she won't meet me.

07:07.560 --> 07:08.800
Just send the card.

07:09.200 --> 07:10.520
What if she ignores it?

07:10.600 --> 07:12.040
Then keep knocking on her door

07:12.120 --> 07:13.480
until she agrees.

07:14.440 --> 07:17.840
After all, she and I have the same goal

07:18.320 --> 07:20.160
not to mention how Zhong Yelan embarrassed her

07:20.240 --> 07:22.080
at the banquet that day.

07:22.920 --> 07:24.400
I don't think she will turn down

07:24.480 --> 07:25.480
an ally like me.

07:28.120 --> 07:29.120
Go on.

07:45.760 --> 07:47.680
Mistress, the Junior Lord of the Wu family

07:47.760 --> 07:49.320
sends another invitation card.

07:49.400 --> 07:51.080
Just ignore him and toss the card aside.

07:58.600 --> 07:59.640
Mistress

07:59.720 --> 08:01.880
why does he keep trying to cotton up to you?

08:02.840 --> 08:04.360
Maybe he thinks

08:04.440 --> 08:06.160
we suffer the same fate

08:06.240 --> 08:08.520
and that we can do something together.

08:08.840 --> 08:10.920
Don't listen to him, Mistress.

08:11.000 --> 08:13.360
He seems scheming.

08:15.360 --> 08:16.640
Of course not.

08:16.720 --> 08:17.720
How can I not see it

08:17.800 --> 08:19.200
since even you have realised it?

08:20.360 --> 08:23.560
I have rejected him so many times

08:23.640 --> 08:25.240
but he just won't give up.

08:25.600 --> 08:26.720
No one loved him in the previous life.

08:26.800 --> 08:27.920
Serves him right.

08:31.160 --> 08:32.160
Mistress.

08:34.760 --> 08:37.240
Is that medicine for your skin?

08:40.640 --> 08:43.080
But it smells a little different.

08:43.400 --> 08:45.160
Don't get so close.

08:45.240 --> 08:46.560
Look how ignorant you are.

08:46.640 --> 08:47.760
Qianzhi.

08:50.680 --> 08:52.320
Mistress made it herself

08:52.400 --> 08:53.520
so, of course, it's different.

08:54.000 --> 08:55.360
You're amazing.

08:55.440 --> 08:56.440
You are good at everything, Mistress.

08:57.440 --> 08:59.760
By the way, Mistress, have you heard?

09:00.800 --> 09:01.800
What?

09:01.880 --> 09:04.360
I heard Hua Man and a low-rank maid

09:04.440 --> 09:06.120
at Zhong's Garden made a blunder

09:06.200 --> 09:08.320
and Lord gave them away to a coachman.

09:08.400 --> 09:09.440
They left the city quietly

09:09.520 --> 09:10.560
early yesterday morning.

09:10.640 --> 09:12.280
I guess they won't be able to come back ever.

09:13.320 --> 09:15.120
Even the maid?

09:15.200 --> 09:16.200
Yeah.

09:16.280 --> 09:18.440
It seems that they made the blunder together

09:18.520 --> 09:20.000
so they were both punished.

09:20.080 --> 09:21.640
I heard the coachman came from

09:21.720 --> 09:23.880
a nomadic tribe far away from here.

09:23.960 --> 09:24.960
This is his last delivery here

09:25.040 --> 09:26.840
and he will not come back again.

09:36.560 --> 09:38.280
Mistress, what's wrong?

09:38.600 --> 09:41.160
Don't you hate Hua Man the most?

09:41.600 --> 09:42.720
Get back to work.

09:54.600 --> 09:55.680
Mistress

09:56.200 --> 09:58.280
Hua Man has herself to blame for attacking...

09:58.960 --> 09:59.960
Lord.

10:00.040 --> 10:01.280
She deserves it.

10:01.600 --> 10:03.680
Otherwise, she would be kicked out at most.

10:05.040 --> 10:06.120
I'm going inside.

10:07.200 --> 10:08.240
It's a bit cold here.

10:32.320 --> 10:33.320
Lord.

10:49.600 --> 10:51.120
After the incense banquet was over

10:51.200 --> 10:52.760
all the butlers left one after another

10:52.840 --> 10:53.920
within ten days.

10:54.520 --> 10:55.840
But the Junior Lord of the Wu family

10:55.920 --> 10:57.520
remains in the city

10:57.920 --> 11:00.200
and pays a visit to Mistress Zhong every day.

11:00.280 --> 11:01.320
She refused to see him

11:01.400 --> 11:02.760
but that didn't stop him.

11:02.840 --> 11:04.120
His intention is unclear.

11:07.560 --> 11:10.280
He asked for a maid at the banquet

11:11.840 --> 11:15.680
and now he's trying to approach Mistress Zhong.

11:15.760 --> 11:20.680
He is a hard-to-read character.

11:20.760 --> 11:22.920
Lord, should I...

11:28.160 --> 11:30.120
How many days will Wu Shuomo be staying?

11:30.760 --> 11:35.000
Lord, he originally planned to come here

11:35.080 --> 11:36.760
for a one-month study tour.

11:37.360 --> 11:39.440
But ten days have passed.

11:40.200 --> 11:41.440
Ignore him then.

11:42.160 --> 11:45.720
I want to see what he's up to.

11:49.120 --> 11:50.840
???Five.                  ???Mistress, let's go.

11:50.920 --> 11:52.040
Seven. Eight.

11:52.120 --> 11:54.400
Mistress, don't stay in the room all day.

11:54.480 --> 11:55.480
You should go out for a walk.

11:55.560 --> 11:57.400
???Eleven.                        ???As you know

11:57.480 --> 11:59.680
that Junior Lord Wu is waiting outside

11:59.760 --> 12:01.720
eager to form an alliance with me.

12:01.800 --> 12:03.000
I'm afraid to go out.

12:03.080 --> 12:04.280
I don't want to run into him.

12:04.360 --> 12:07.120
But you can't sit in the room all day.

12:07.640 --> 12:09.240
Why not kick the shuttlecock with us?

12:09.320 --> 12:11.800
Maybe it will cheer you up.

12:13.600 --> 12:15.400
Seeing you depressed every day

12:15.480 --> 12:16.680
makes us feel terrible.

12:16.760 --> 12:18.000
Yeah.

12:18.080 --> 12:19.160
Join us.

12:19.240 --> 12:20.280
???Right?                ???Let's play together.

12:20.720 --> 12:21.960
Join us, Mistress.

12:22.360 --> 12:23.720
Come on...

12:24.080 --> 12:25.200
Do it, Mistress.

12:52.960 --> 12:53.960
Over here.

12:57.120 --> 12:58.600
Are you all right, Guard Hua?

12:58.680 --> 13:00.120
???Yeah.                                  ???Go!

13:00.200 --> 13:01.200
Let's go.

13:19.000 --> 13:21.080
Are you sweating?

13:24.560 --> 13:26.640
It's a scorching day today.

13:27.480 --> 13:29.960
Mistress, if you feel hot

13:30.040 --> 13:31.760
go inside and rest.

13:32.680 --> 13:34.200
I've been staying in the room for too long

13:34.280 --> 13:35.560
and my body is getting weaker.

13:35.840 --> 13:37.880
It's good for me to enjoy the sun here.

13:38.160 --> 13:40.960
All right then. Let me put this in there.

13:41.040 --> 13:42.040
All right.

14:18.960 --> 14:20.680
Can one of you get Hua Rongzhou over here?

14:20.760 --> 14:21.760
Let me...

14:21.840 --> 14:22.920
Let me do it.

14:34.640 --> 14:35.680
Greetings, Mistress.

14:36.440 --> 14:37.720
Make yourself comfortable.

14:37.800 --> 14:39.760
You don't have to bow to me

14:39.840 --> 14:42.040
when there are only us.

14:42.920 --> 14:44.400
Nothing much.

14:45.040 --> 14:46.040
It's just I see you

14:46.120 --> 14:47.480
guarding the entrance here every day

14:47.560 --> 14:49.040
and no one takes turns with you.

14:49.120 --> 14:50.240
I just want to tell you

14:50.320 --> 14:52.680
that you can come here once every other day.

14:53.400 --> 14:55.520
I am the guard of your compound, Mistress.

14:56.160 --> 14:57.680
How can I leave my post without authorisation?

14:58.280 --> 14:59.280
It's all right.

14:59.360 --> 15:01.400
There are so many guards coming and going.

15:01.480 --> 15:02.720
Nothing bad will happen.

15:03.200 --> 15:05.800
Life is short.

15:05.880 --> 15:07.120
And you are so young.

15:07.200 --> 15:09.520
There must be something that you want to do.

15:09.600 --> 15:12.120
Don't waste your time working as a guard.

15:13.160 --> 15:14.440
Something I want to do?

15:15.640 --> 15:18.640
Yeah. Do what you want to do.

15:18.720 --> 15:21.120
If I'm in need, I'll send for you.

15:28.560 --> 15:29.880
How rare!

15:30.400 --> 15:31.760
I didn't expect to see him here.

15:32.800 --> 15:33.920
Yeah.

15:34.000 --> 15:37.360
I thought he was too afraid to come here.

15:38.000 --> 15:39.680
He already looks like a woman

15:39.760 --> 15:41.720
and he hangs out with women every day.

15:43.600 --> 15:45.120
???Want to spar?                 ???Sounds good.

15:45.800 --> 15:46.800
Bring it on.

15:53.320 --> 15:54.760
Care to join them?

16:27.400 --> 16:29.000
???Yeah. Easy does it.                  ???Stop!

16:32.040 --> 16:34.480
Not me. I'm not going to spar with you.

16:39.040 --> 16:41.440
Nice moves!

16:41.520 --> 16:43.160
I knew that you were good during recruitment.

16:43.240 --> 16:44.800
Let me spar with you

16:44.880 --> 16:45.880
and see how much progress you have made

16:45.960 --> 16:46.960
in the past few months.

16:47.040 --> 16:48.360
Yes, Chief.

16:50.320 --> 16:51.320
The needle should go in here.

16:55.560 --> 16:57.040
Make the snitch smaller.

16:59.440 --> 17:01.640
Mistress, how about taking a rest

17:01.720 --> 17:02.840
and carrying on another day?

17:05.480 --> 17:06.560
Mistress.

17:07.680 --> 17:08.800
Mistress.

17:10.320 --> 17:11.960
I heard a fight went down at the training ground

17:12.040 --> 17:14.440
and Guard Hua was so skilful

17:14.520 --> 17:16.640
that he even defeated the veterans.

17:16.720 --> 17:17.920
Really?

17:18.240 --> 17:20.520
He's only been here for half a year, no?

17:20.600 --> 17:21.960
You will be surprised, Mistress.

17:22.040 --> 17:23.880
Even Master praised him today

17:23.960 --> 17:25.960
saying that he drew with Nanfeng

17:26.040 --> 17:27.520
after learning just a few moves from him.

17:27.880 --> 17:30.000
The moment I laid eyes on him

17:30.280 --> 17:31.840
I knew he was an extraordinary man.

17:33.680 --> 17:35.040
That was because Nanfeng held back.

17:35.120 --> 17:36.360
You're an unmarried girl.

17:36.440 --> 17:38.120
Don't you feel embarrassed saying those words?

17:38.920 --> 17:41.600
Nanfeng is the highest-ranked guard

17:41.680 --> 17:43.680
so he must be good at martial arts.

17:43.760 --> 17:44.760
Yeah.

17:44.840 --> 17:46.960
So it means Guard Hua is really outstanding.

17:48.160 --> 17:49.360
How shameless.

17:50.040 --> 17:51.880
???Don't say that!         ???You are shameless.

17:51.960 --> 17:53.200
???Don't say that!         ???You are shameless.

17:53.280 --> 17:54.840
???Stop saying that!                 ???You are!

17:55.000 --> 17:56.680
You... that's not true at all.

17:56.760 --> 17:59.040
Hua Rongzhou, come here.

18:07.440 --> 18:08.520
Mistress.

18:09.760 --> 18:11.080
Did something good happen?

18:11.160 --> 18:12.720
You seem to be in a good mood.

18:13.200 --> 18:15.960
You finally remember my name, Mistress.

18:16.880 --> 18:18.560
Have I ever forgotten it?

18:23.800 --> 18:25.280
I heard from Cuizhu

18:25.360 --> 18:26.360
that you drew with Nanfeng

18:26.440 --> 18:27.440
in a sparring session.

18:27.680 --> 18:30.880
I think that was because the chief held back.

18:31.840 --> 18:33.520
Not only are you talented in martial arts

18:33.600 --> 18:35.160
but you're also modest.

18:35.400 --> 18:36.760
Cuizhu has good taste.

18:39.680 --> 18:41.000
Mistress.

19:03.280 --> 19:04.600
Do you know

19:04.680 --> 19:06.760
where the best artisan shop in the city is?

19:07.760 --> 19:09.400
I heard that there was a female craftsman

19:09.480 --> 19:11.120
named Wei Xian.

19:11.200 --> 19:12.840
She was the most skilled.

19:13.800 --> 19:15.000
A female craftsman?

19:15.080 --> 19:17.160
I have never heard of this person.

19:18.080 --> 19:19.760
You don't know her, Mistress?

19:20.200 --> 19:23.000
All the girls admired her.

19:23.800 --> 19:26.160
Unfortunately, she passed away a while ago.

19:27.320 --> 19:29.600
I don't know about other stores.

19:29.680 --> 19:31.560
Shall I ask Guard Hua to ask around?

19:31.640 --> 19:33.280
No. Don't tell him.

19:33.880 --> 19:35.040
Go and ask around yourself

19:35.120 --> 19:36.120
and be quick.

19:37.080 --> 19:38.080
All right.

19:48.080 --> 19:49.160
You're back from the training?

19:50.160 --> 19:51.480
We're eating and drinking.

19:52.120 --> 19:53.520
Do you want to join us?

19:56.960 --> 19:57.960
Are you sure you don't want some?

19:58.040 --> 19:59.960
???Have some.              ???Have some with us.

20:05.960 --> 20:07.640
Look at how defiant he is.

20:08.360 --> 20:09.360
What else can we do?

20:09.840 --> 20:11.400
He's proficient with martial arts.

20:11.680 --> 20:14.000
I'd say it was because the chief was lenient.

20:14.080 --> 20:16.000
He held back, that was how it ended up in a tie.

20:16.280 --> 20:20.560
I feel it's unclear who held back.

20:21.040 --> 20:22.040
Let's drop it.

20:22.120 --> 20:24.240
Enough about that grumpy man.

20:24.320 --> 20:25.520
Come on. Drink up.

20:32.200 --> 20:33.720
Speaking of the chief

20:34.120 --> 20:35.640
have you heard the rumour?

20:36.280 --> 20:39.160
You mean the one related to Mistress?

20:39.880 --> 20:42.120
???Lower your voice.                 ???No need.

20:42.200 --> 20:44.120
Everyone in the house knows about it.

20:44.200 --> 20:46.080
???Keep it down.                     ???But yes.

20:46.160 --> 20:49.000
When Master ordered to cut spending

20:49.280 --> 20:50.680
the chief immediately went to Butler Ji

20:50.760 --> 20:52.840
to reason with him.

20:52.920 --> 20:56.000
He's Master's personal guard. How could he...

20:57.960 --> 20:59.120
It's really unbelievable.

20:59.200 --> 21:00.320
Enough...

21:00.640 --> 21:01.880
It's not a good thing.

21:01.960 --> 21:03.520
Don't talk about it anymore. Let's drink.

21:11.080 --> 21:12.240
She still won't see me?

21:12.320 --> 21:13.320
No, she won't.

21:13.400 --> 21:15.720
Mistress Zhong says she's not well enough

21:15.800 --> 21:16.880
to receive guests.

21:17.680 --> 21:19.360
She's unwell?

21:19.880 --> 21:22.560
But she looked energetic when I saw her.

21:22.880 --> 21:24.720
Before coming to Huangcheng

21:24.800 --> 21:26.840
you swore that you would just come here

21:26.920 --> 21:27.920
for the formula

21:28.000 --> 21:29.640
of the Zhong family's Jiayin Pill.

21:29.960 --> 21:32.640
Half a month has passed.

21:33.160 --> 21:34.320
Instead of searching for the formula

21:34.400 --> 21:36.080
you're searching for someone.

21:36.160 --> 21:38.320
If the Senior Lord knows about this...

21:39.440 --> 21:40.880
Don't use my father to threaten me.

21:41.200 --> 21:42.360
Who is your master?

21:42.440 --> 21:44.360
Of course, it's you.

21:45.120 --> 21:48.120
But we have to go back in ten days

21:48.200 --> 21:49.600
so let's just forget it.

21:51.160 --> 21:54.520
I'll find someone else who can lend me a hand.

22:01.840 --> 22:04.960
Enjoy and drink as much as you like.

22:05.320 --> 22:06.520
This is my treat.

22:07.080 --> 22:09.880
Your generosity befits your status

22:09.960 --> 22:12.480
as the son of the butler of the Zhong family.

22:13.240 --> 22:16.040
I'm the only son of my parents

22:16.520 --> 22:17.600
and everything my father owns

22:20.680 --> 22:23.800
will be mine.

22:23.880 --> 22:25.880
Treating you to a meal is nothing to speak of.

22:26.320 --> 22:27.800
That's right.

22:28.280 --> 22:32.840
It's really rare to see Miss Jiaojiao.

22:33.920 --> 22:36.480
You're incredible! I'm impressed.

22:37.200 --> 22:38.200
Jiaojiao.

22:40.840 --> 22:43.840
You haven't been around. This is nothing.

22:48.960 --> 22:50.160
What audacity! Who are you?

22:53.400 --> 22:54.720
It's you, Junior Lord Wu.

22:54.800 --> 22:57.880
It's really you, Young Master Hua.

22:57.960 --> 22:59.360
I thought I heard it wrong

22:59.440 --> 23:00.840
when I was standing at the door.

23:00.920 --> 23:02.640
This is the Junior Lord of the Wu family.

23:04.200 --> 23:06.800
???Nice to meet you.        ???Nice to meet you.

23:06.880 --> 23:08.960
???Please take a seat.                ???Please.

23:09.040 --> 23:10.040
Be quick.

23:10.400 --> 23:11.480
Young Master Hua

23:11.560 --> 23:13.880
you left a deep impression on me

23:13.960 --> 23:15.920
at the incense banquet.

23:17.440 --> 23:19.560
I wanted to make friends with you

23:19.840 --> 23:22.400
but couldn't find a good way to approach you.

23:22.840 --> 23:24.760
Oh, I'm flattered.

23:24.840 --> 23:28.520
I also felt like you were an old friend

23:28.600 --> 23:29.600
at the first meeting.

23:29.680 --> 23:30.680
Exactly.

23:30.760 --> 23:32.040
???Yes... glad to meet you.           ???Cheers.

23:32.120 --> 23:33.120
Come on.

23:36.880 --> 23:38.680
Jiaojiao, go serve Junior Lord Wu.

23:41.480 --> 23:42.720
???No need.                   ???Junior Lord Wu.

23:43.040 --> 23:46.080
This kind of uncultured woman

23:46.160 --> 23:47.400
is not my type.

23:47.680 --> 23:48.680
Go back to where you were.

23:51.920 --> 23:53.080
Come on, let's drink.

23:53.160 --> 23:54.600
Junior Lord Wu, are you saying

23:54.680 --> 23:57.600
you can't forget

23:57.680 --> 24:00.240
the maid of Master Zhong?

24:04.600 --> 24:05.720
It was a pity

24:07.400 --> 24:10.640
that someone stopped me.

24:11.520 --> 24:12.640
I think

24:13.120 --> 24:15.240
my brother-in-law went too far.

24:15.800 --> 24:18.640
She's just a maid.

24:18.720 --> 24:20.120
Why can't he give her to you?

24:20.560 --> 24:22.000
He already has my sister as his wife.

24:22.080 --> 24:23.960
Why does he still think about other women?

24:24.040 --> 24:25.120
Exactly.

24:25.440 --> 24:26.880
Mistress Zhong is the most talented woman

24:26.960 --> 24:28.400
in the city

24:29.040 --> 24:30.600
and is famous all over the world.

24:30.680 --> 24:33.920
Master Zhong has bad taste.

24:34.360 --> 24:36.880
It's a pity I came here late

24:37.240 --> 24:40.120
and she's already married to him.

24:40.200 --> 24:44.080
Otherwise, I would compete with him.

24:44.160 --> 24:47.320
I couldn't agree more.

24:47.400 --> 24:49.960
My sister is the prettiest girl in the world.

24:50.280 --> 24:54.440
Who can compare to her?

24:54.960 --> 24:55.960
Can you?

24:56.240 --> 24:57.400
You're stating the obvious.

24:59.080 --> 25:01.960
Anyway, if my father hadn't stopped me

25:02.040 --> 25:03.400
I would have rushed into Zhong Residence

25:03.480 --> 25:05.200
and give Master Zhong a beating.

25:05.480 --> 25:08.160
My sentiments exactly!

25:09.240 --> 25:10.400
Speaking of which

25:11.040 --> 25:13.360
I want to talk to Mistress Zhong.

25:13.440 --> 25:16.040
If she allows me to take away the maid

25:16.120 --> 25:18.760
that will pull out the thorn in her side

25:19.440 --> 25:21.480
and she will live more comfortably

25:21.560 --> 25:23.720
in Zhong Residence. Am I right?

25:26.040 --> 25:28.240
My sister is smart

25:28.640 --> 25:30.320
but I don't think she can make decisions

25:30.400 --> 25:31.920
for my brother-in-law.

25:35.400 --> 25:36.480
It's not hard

25:36.640 --> 25:38.560
to find a way to satisfy both of them.

25:38.640 --> 25:42.080
But Mistress Zhong has been

25:42.160 --> 25:43.520
staying in the house for some time.

25:43.600 --> 25:46.160
I wonder, Young Master Hua...

25:48.240 --> 25:49.280
Brother Hua...

25:50.240 --> 25:52.360
if you can introduce me to her.

25:56.840 --> 25:58.520
Look at your face. It's so red.

25:58.600 --> 25:59.600
Furong is quite pretty.

25:59.680 --> 26:01.520
I beg to differ.

26:01.600 --> 26:02.720
???She's mine.       ???There are prettier ones.

26:02.800 --> 26:03.960
She's mine.

26:06.040 --> 26:07.200
Junior Lord Wu

26:07.280 --> 26:09.520
are you really not going to my house?

26:10.480 --> 26:11.560
No.

26:13.400 --> 26:14.680
We're leaving then.

26:15.320 --> 26:17.080
???Goodbye.                          ???Goodbye.

26:17.160 --> 26:18.200
???Goodbye.                          ???Goodbye.

26:18.600 --> 26:20.320
???Go...                      ???I'm telling you

26:20.400 --> 26:22.800
Huang has prepared dinner for us.

26:22.880 --> 26:23.920
Let's continue drinking.

26:25.320 --> 26:27.000
???Let's drink!               ???Furong is mine.

26:27.080 --> 26:28.360
???Right. She's yours.                ???Master.

26:29.120 --> 26:30.920
???How is it going?               ???She's mine.

26:32.560 --> 26:36.000
Brother Hua, could you introduce me to her?

26:37.440 --> 26:39.520
I can't make decisions for her.

26:40.160 --> 26:43.280
She is a very independent woman.

26:43.360 --> 26:44.920
If I do it without telling her

26:45.000 --> 26:46.680
she will be angry.

26:46.960 --> 26:49.200
She isn't an ordinary woman.

26:49.600 --> 26:52.080
If Jiaojiao is angry

26:52.160 --> 26:55.240
all I need to do is buy her some makeup.

26:55.320 --> 26:57.200
But my sister is different.

26:57.280 --> 26:59.040
If I make her angry

26:59.120 --> 27:01.000
she'll ignore me

27:01.520 --> 27:03.080
no matter how much jewellery I buy her.

27:04.120 --> 27:05.440
He looks stupid

27:05.840 --> 27:07.320
but actually, he's not.

27:08.400 --> 27:09.560
If there is no other way

27:10.400 --> 27:13.240
I'll have to sneak into Zhong Residence myself.

27:16.040 --> 27:18.080
Zhong Residence

27:27.280 --> 27:28.520
Since you are here today

27:28.600 --> 27:29.800
let's spar another round.

27:30.120 --> 27:31.960
This time I won't show mercy.

27:32.400 --> 27:35.560
He is Master's personal guard. How could he...

27:36.280 --> 27:37.680
It's unbelievable.

27:37.760 --> 27:38.760
All right.

27:38.920 --> 27:39.920
Remember.

27:40.160 --> 27:41.800
We will stop before going too far.

28:38.520 --> 28:39.520
No.

28:49.920 --> 28:51.120
Well done.

28:51.200 --> 28:52.360
Just as I expected.

28:52.960 --> 28:54.760
You didn't give it your all the last time.

28:54.840 --> 28:55.840
Why?

28:56.640 --> 28:57.800
Please forgive me, Chief.

28:59.360 --> 29:00.760
Tell me. Why did you hold back

29:00.840 --> 29:02.120
the last time you sparred with me?

29:03.440 --> 29:04.440
The person

29:06.200 --> 29:07.840
who taught me martial arts

29:07.920 --> 29:09.000
told me to do that.

29:09.080 --> 29:10.080
Your martial arts teacher?

29:10.160 --> 29:11.160
What does he do?

29:13.320 --> 29:15.400
Forget it. I'm going to tell Master right now

29:15.480 --> 29:17.680
that he has recruited a martial arts prodigy.

29:38.080 --> 29:41.640
Come on! Welcome back, our victor!

29:41.720 --> 29:43.520
Welcome back...

29:43.800 --> 29:45.280
You're awesome, Guard Hua.

30:06.960 --> 30:08.080
All right.

30:09.200 --> 30:10.600
Mistress, you have something to tell me?

30:10.680 --> 30:12.880
Yes. We all heard

30:12.960 --> 30:14.760
that you defeated Nanfeng today.

30:14.840 --> 30:17.800
Yeah. So we're celebrating for you.

30:18.360 --> 30:20.480
???Qianzhi.                    ???Yes, Mistress.

30:25.280 --> 30:26.280
Mistress.

30:28.240 --> 30:30.080
This is a reward for you.

30:30.160 --> 30:31.240
Open it.

30:41.600 --> 30:43.880
This is custom-made

30:43.960 --> 30:45.120
from the best store in the city.

30:45.720 --> 30:47.120
I noticed you were still using

30:47.200 --> 30:48.800
a house-issued sabre.

30:49.320 --> 30:51.960
You're now the only guard in my compound

30:52.040 --> 30:53.040
not to mention

30:53.120 --> 30:55.160
that your skills are on par with Nanfeng's

30:55.240 --> 30:57.200
so we can't have you using an inferior weapon.

30:58.440 --> 30:59.600
You work for me

30:59.680 --> 31:02.160
and I promise you won't be disappointed.

31:02.240 --> 31:04.120
You can get whatever you want.

31:09.760 --> 31:12.280
What did you do? Who did this?

31:12.360 --> 31:14.200
Why are there so many petals on the ground?

31:14.280 --> 31:15.400
I merely went out for a while

31:15.480 --> 31:17.040
and you turned this place upside down.

31:17.120 --> 31:18.120
Hurry up and clear up the mess.

31:18.200 --> 31:19.640
???Right away!               ???We'll do it now.

31:19.960 --> 31:20.960
Get a broom.

31:21.040 --> 31:22.320
Go, go. A broom.

31:22.400 --> 31:23.880
Yeah. Be quick.

31:27.680 --> 31:29.480
These girls...

31:29.560 --> 31:31.240
are really a pain in the neck.

31:47.320 --> 31:48.320
Thank you.

31:49.760 --> 31:50.800
Thank you, Mistress.

31:51.680 --> 31:53.440
It's all right. Hope you like it.

31:54.960 --> 31:57.000
This is the first time I received a gift.

31:58.400 --> 31:59.400
I like it very much.

32:20.120 --> 32:23.960
Nothing has changed in the last half month?

32:24.560 --> 32:25.680
Yes.

32:26.080 --> 32:27.280
It seems that Master and Mistress

32:27.360 --> 32:30.760
haven't spoken much to each other these days.

32:32.960 --> 32:36.120
They are still angry with each other.

32:36.800 --> 32:39.120
I don't know.

32:40.200 --> 32:41.800
Go tell Qian

32:42.440 --> 32:45.320
to come over tomorrow.

32:46.200 --> 32:47.600
I'll ask her about it.

32:48.440 --> 32:50.560
Your Highness, didn't you say

32:51.120 --> 32:53.160
it was Master's own business?

32:53.920 --> 32:56.760
Are you going to do something about it now?

33:05.800 --> 33:06.800
Your Highness.

33:09.280 --> 33:10.840
Is the wedding banquet over?

33:12.160 --> 33:15.840
I heard Master got drunk

33:16.120 --> 33:17.400
and slept in his study last night.

33:19.240 --> 33:20.920
He can't blame that on anyone.

33:21.480 --> 33:23.760
He was pretty dumb to fall for that trick.

33:24.280 --> 33:26.800
Since you know about it

33:26.880 --> 33:28.880
why didn't you tell him, Your Highness?

33:28.960 --> 33:31.080
Maybe he would change his mind.

33:31.160 --> 33:33.680
It's his own business

33:33.760 --> 33:35.760
and he is convinced that

33:35.840 --> 33:37.280
the daughter of the Hua family

33:37.360 --> 33:39.240
is innocent and kind.

33:40.440 --> 33:42.000
I have no evidence

33:42.600 --> 33:44.000
so what can I say?

33:45.800 --> 33:47.680
It is not going to be easy for Master.

33:47.760 --> 33:51.640
Let's hope that Hua Qian will stop

33:51.720 --> 33:53.680
doing things like that

33:54.360 --> 33:56.880
and will not bring us trouble again.

33:57.320 --> 34:00.240
How did a young lady like her

34:00.320 --> 34:03.600
learn these dirty tricks?

34:04.240 --> 34:06.200
Now that they are married

34:06.280 --> 34:07.840
I suppose she will gradually

34:07.920 --> 34:11.120
become more mature and demure.

34:13.040 --> 34:14.080
We shall see.

34:14.840 --> 34:17.680
When they come here to greet me tomorrow

34:17.760 --> 34:21.920
I will see how mature she has become.

34:23.040 --> 34:25.560
Most people come to my place

34:26.200 --> 34:30.040
because they want something.

34:30.400 --> 34:31.640
There's rarely someone

34:31.720 --> 34:33.000
who doesn't want anything.

34:33.560 --> 34:36.200
All she does is talk with me.

34:36.480 --> 34:41.200
I can speak freely with her.

34:41.920 --> 34:43.080
All right.

34:43.160 --> 34:46.400
I will get someone to tell her.

34:46.480 --> 34:47.520
Go ahead.

35:01.480 --> 35:02.560
Is this piece of news reliable?

35:03.120 --> 35:05.120
Master, yes it is.

35:06.200 --> 35:07.320
That's great.

35:07.720 --> 35:09.960
I guess she has nowhere to run this time.

35:14.720 --> 35:15.880
Greetings, Mistress.

35:16.400 --> 35:17.400
Take a seat.

35:18.640 --> 35:19.640
Yes, Mistress.

35:25.680 --> 35:27.720
I heard that you hadn't been

35:27.800 --> 35:29.840
out of the house in the past few days.

35:30.640 --> 35:33.080
I felt tired

35:33.160 --> 35:35.160
so I just stayed in the house.

35:35.240 --> 35:36.600
That's not good.

35:36.680 --> 35:38.600
As Mistress of the Zhong family

35:38.680 --> 35:40.640
you have the duty to enhance Yelan's reputation

35:40.720 --> 35:43.720
so you should go out and socialise more often.

35:43.800 --> 35:45.360
A mistress

35:46.160 --> 35:49.560
should not stay confined to her compound.

35:49.880 --> 35:53.320
She should often interact

35:53.400 --> 35:55.560
with the wives of other distinguished men.

35:56.240 --> 35:57.440
Yes.

35:57.520 --> 35:58.640
One more thing.

35:58.720 --> 36:01.080
You should pay more attention

36:01.520 --> 36:03.880
to what Yelan did

36:04.760 --> 36:06.520
at the incense banquet.

36:07.320 --> 36:08.480
You are too young.

36:08.560 --> 36:11.000
There are many things you don't understand.

36:11.880 --> 36:13.720
Feelings of love or gratitude

36:14.000 --> 36:16.440
between a couple

36:16.840 --> 36:19.640
tend to fade over time.

36:19.720 --> 36:24.760
Holding power firmly in your hands

36:24.840 --> 36:26.880
is key to a long-lasting marriage.

36:28.320 --> 36:29.800
Thank you for your advice, Mistress.

36:30.880 --> 36:35.680
That maid is called Mu Yao, right?

36:36.320 --> 36:38.360
How are you going to deal with her?

36:38.880 --> 36:40.200
Master likes her.

36:40.520 --> 36:42.440
I don't wish to go against his will.

36:43.880 --> 36:46.720
You have to keep a close eye on things at home.

36:46.800 --> 36:48.280
Otherwise, even a maid

36:48.360 --> 36:50.440
could crawl onto her master's bed.

36:50.720 --> 36:52.200
Mu Yao is not that kind of person.

36:52.560 --> 36:54.280
Your Highness, you have no idea.

36:54.360 --> 36:57.920
Mu Yao has never once seduced Master.

36:58.000 --> 37:00.320
You'll stop thinking this way

37:00.400 --> 37:02.400
once you meet Mu Yao.

37:02.680 --> 37:04.760
Why are you still taking her side?

37:05.360 --> 37:07.080
I'm just stating the facts.

37:07.360 --> 37:09.880
I don't want you to misjudge anyone.

37:14.360 --> 37:19.080
How come you have become so soft?

37:22.560 --> 37:24.040
That's the reality.

37:24.120 --> 37:25.560
There's no point in me putting up a fight.

37:27.640 --> 37:31.040
You almost lost your life saving Yelan.

37:31.120 --> 37:33.440
He went too far this time.

37:33.520 --> 37:36.000
You are his legitimate wife

37:36.080 --> 37:38.600
so he shouldn't have done this to you.

37:38.880 --> 37:41.080
If you feel you can't speak up

37:41.400 --> 37:43.080
I'll talk to him for you.

37:43.160 --> 37:44.520
Mistress, you know how

37:44.600 --> 37:47.240
I managed to marry Master, don't you?

37:50.160 --> 37:51.160
You...

37:55.640 --> 37:57.080
Don't change the subject.

37:57.160 --> 37:59.240
I'm talking about the maid.

38:00.760 --> 38:02.160
As his legitimate wife

38:02.240 --> 38:05.080
you should assert your authority.

38:05.640 --> 38:08.600
You shouldn't just stand by and do nothing.

38:11.880 --> 38:14.760
Mistress, may I ask you to pass down an order?

38:15.280 --> 38:16.280
What order?

38:16.720 --> 38:19.600
Master and Mu Yao are in love with each other

38:19.680 --> 38:21.480
so could you give the order

38:21.560 --> 38:23.560
to make her Master's concubine?

38:24.200 --> 38:25.200
You...

38:27.160 --> 38:28.160
Do you...

38:28.520 --> 38:29.760
Do you really mean that?

38:30.640 --> 38:31.640
Yes.

38:40.280 --> 38:42.440
She will just be a concubine.

38:42.840 --> 38:44.600
You're his legitimate wife.

38:44.680 --> 38:48.000
I'll leave it to you to decide.

38:48.800 --> 38:52.600
But could you please do it for me?

38:52.680 --> 38:55.880
Otherwise, Master might get the wrong idea.

38:56.400 --> 38:57.480
All right.

38:58.040 --> 38:59.600
Your wish is granted.

39:00.200 --> 39:01.640
I'll send someone to Zhong Residence tomorrow

39:01.720 --> 39:02.720
to pass down the order.

39:04.040 --> 39:05.240
Thank you very much, Mistress.

39:13.760 --> 39:15.280
Have some of this.

39:23.720 --> 39:26.240
You have a good appetite today, Your Highness.

39:29.200 --> 39:31.440
A weight has been lifted off my shoulders

39:31.880 --> 39:33.560
so I feel much better.

39:37.600 --> 39:38.600
Since she suggested that

39:38.680 --> 39:40.400
Yelan marries a concubine

39:40.760 --> 39:41.960
it means

39:42.040 --> 39:44.080
she wants to get back together with him.

39:45.320 --> 39:46.440
That's true.

39:47.360 --> 39:51.480
Mistress is truly giving.

39:51.560 --> 39:53.040
She has to figure out

39:53.120 --> 39:55.480
how to run the household by herself.

39:56.400 --> 39:59.320
We all learn from painful experiences

39:59.600 --> 40:02.040
I can give some advice at most.

40:03.200 --> 40:05.360
I'm glad she heeded my advice.

40:06.000 --> 40:09.040
Yes. Your Highness, you offered her

40:09.120 --> 40:11.440
invaluable advice.

40:11.520 --> 40:13.560
Stop buttering me up.

40:24.400 --> 40:26.320
Mistress, why did you ask Her Highness

40:26.400 --> 40:27.920
to take a concubine for Master?

40:28.000 --> 40:29.800
You're too kind to Mu Yao.

40:30.400 --> 40:31.880
It just occurred to me

40:32.200 --> 40:34.600
that there was a simple and direct way

40:34.680 --> 40:36.280
to make Zhong Yelan understand something.

40:36.960 --> 40:38.080
Understand what?

40:38.160 --> 40:39.960
There's no room for two of us.

40:41.120 --> 40:42.120
I'll even make it a grand wedding

40:42.200 --> 40:43.640
when he takes her as his concubine

40:44.040 --> 40:45.400
then he will know

40:45.480 --> 40:47.600
he cannot avoid the problem.

40:47.880 --> 40:49.400
He knows that

40:49.480 --> 40:52.520
Mu Yao and I can never share a husband.

40:52.600 --> 40:55.600
So if he wants to live a chaotic life

40:55.680 --> 40:57.400
he can continue to keep me in Zhong Residence.

40:58.600 --> 41:01.640
Mistress, why don't you just drive her away?

41:01.720 --> 41:02.800
Why must you take it lying down

41:02.880 --> 41:03.960
and make her happy?

41:04.040 --> 41:05.120
Drive her away?

41:05.400 --> 41:06.960
It's easier said than done.

41:07.640 --> 41:09.640
They are like two magnets.

41:09.720 --> 41:11.320
The more you try to separate them

41:11.400 --> 41:12.680
the tighter they get.

41:17.960 --> 41:20.920
Is it Mistress Zhong in the carriage ahead?

41:34.880 --> 41:37.360
Lord, they've been dealt with.

41:38.440 --> 41:39.600
Go to the physician and get me

41:39.680 --> 41:41.200
another bottle of Jinhua Powder.

41:41.360 --> 41:42.840
Do you feel unwell, Lord?

41:42.920 --> 41:44.360
I'm fine. It's just...

41:47.960 --> 41:48.960
for emergencies.

41:54.080 --> 41:55.400
